dictionary.description: The Prime Minister of the Randall Empire who has carried out many reforms in her time, and yet never fails to prepare for whatever sudden crisis may befall her home regardless of all the pressure she faces. Initially the daughter of a noble household who was once part of the Imperial Guard, Paris eventually decided to work for the Akras Summoners' Hall instead after having experienced many battles alongside the Legendary Summoner. However, following her own path ultimately led her to leave Summoners' Hall and enter the Empire's political scene, a difficult and arduous road to take. After fighting one senior politician after another, she gained the support of the people and became the first female Prime Minister in the history of the Empire, bringing with her an era of reform and change.
dictionary.evolution:
The road ahead is long,
but I trust in the strength of my will
and the support of those who believe in me.
dictionary.fusion:
I will not give up, my friend taught me not to.
I'll keep going, especially if I can count on my comrades to stick by me.
dictionary.summon: I'm still looking for the right answer. I don't want to settle on one correct ideology, but instead help open a path to new possibilities.
